OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FIt will be another fine dry
OL,6,Fday with plenty of sunshine though
OL,7,Fhigh cloud may turn the sunshine hazy
OL,8,Flater. Very warm with some cooling sea
OL,9,Fbreezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,12,Fand warm on Friday, chance of showers
OL,13,Fin north. Saturday cloudy and cooler,
OL,14,Fthen becoming bright with some
OL,15,Fsunshine on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
